    <div class="our-story">
        <h2>OUR STORY</h2>
        <p>At Fiora, we believe that bags are more than just accessories. They're an extension of your identity, your
            style, and your attitude. That's why we go beyond creating beautiful bags – we craft experiences that
            resonate with the bold and confident Gen Z woman.</p>
        <p>A Fiora bag is not just a bag on your arm – it's a statement. It's the confidence that comes with knowing you
            look polished and put together. It's the empowerment that lets you conquer your day, knowing you have a
            reliable companion by your side. We want our bags to be more than just possessions; we want them to be
            partners in your journey. Explore our collections and discover the Fiora experience – where style meets
            confidence, and every journey is an adventure.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="gallery">
        <div class="zoom-effect">
            <img src="/images/aboutbanner2.png" alt="Fiora Bags Collection 1">
        </div>
        <div class="zoom-effect">
            <img src="/images/aboutusbanner3.jpg" alt="Fiora Bags Collection 2">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="vision-mission">
        <div class="mission">
            <h2>MISSION</h2>
            <p>Fiora is a new-age fashion brand that is committed to delivering high-quality and trending products at an
                accessible price point. Our mission is to empower Gen Z women to express themselves through fashion
                without compromising on quality and trends. We believe that exceptional design and craftsmanship should
                be accessible to all.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="vision">
            <h2>VISION</h2>
            <p>Our vision is to become a global leader by making premium trendsetting products accessible to a larger
                set of audience. We aim to be the go-to brand for Gen Z women who seek fashionable, functional, and
                sustainable accessories that reflect their personality and values. We strive to create a community where
                young women feel confident, empowered, and inspired.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="attention-to-detail">
        <h2>ATTENTION TO DETAIL</h2>
        <p>We carefully craft each piece with utmost care. By keeping the modern Gen Z woman in mind, we understand your
            need for empowerment, style, and functionality. So, every stitch, every pocket, and every curve is
            thoughtfully constructed to seamlessly integrate into your life. Our designs blend contemporary aesthetics
            with practical functionality, ensuring that your Fiora bag not only looks stunning but also serves your
            everyday needs.</p>
    </div>

